{"title":"筑起东海铁长城","authors":["福建惠安县崇武镇渔民民兵业余演出队集体创作"],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":8,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起东海铁长城（多口词）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"福建惠安县崇武镇渔民民兵业余演出队集体创作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光东方升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海螺响连声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗迎风飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们来练兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热烈响应毛主席的伟大号召，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向亦工亦农亦文亦武的革命化方向前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心向首都北京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对波涛千万顷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海前线崇武人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起一道铁长城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海那边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"台湾海峡浊浪滚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父兄的血债要算清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚非拉美风云急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贤良江畔有炮声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上三分之二的人民没解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的担子真不轻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着五洲四海风云变幻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话牢记在心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对付凶恶的美帝国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须实行人民战争。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民皆兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民战争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是对付侵略者的法宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是人类解放的途径。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们得到了解放；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠着它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们战无不胜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打败日本法西斯强盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭了八百万蒋匪兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"垂死的美帝国主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也将在人民战争的海洋里没顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民皆兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民战争！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世代继承。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们永远紧握手中枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是东海前线的民兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们勇敢顽强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕牺牲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们牢记毛主席的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天勤练兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇武人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤练兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳武结合好方针。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风狂水冷心里热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日晒雨淋志坚定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东海宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我敢登。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星光浪影认得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶浪千层要踩平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时刻紧握手中枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风大浪里练出真本领。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀敢见红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举枪灭流萤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投弹远又准，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战术快又精。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人从那里来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们一定在那里把他消灭干净！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}